text: Fynn Arkenberg (born 4 March 1996) is a German footballer who plays as a centre-back for SV Rödinghausen. ==Club career== Arkenberg is a youth exponent from Hannover 96. He made his Bundesliga debut on 7 May 2016 against TSG 1899 Hoffenheim.
